sentences: COP18/CMP 8 President, Al-Attiyah reminded parties of the practice since COP 1 of applying the draft rules of procedure (FCCC/CP/1996/2) with the exception of draft rule 42 on voting, which has remained unresolved since COP 1.
He informed parties that no consensus has been achieved after consultations held by the COP 17 President, and parties agreed to apply the draft rules with the exception of draft rule 42.
